siestaXC library

Copyright (c) (1996-2009) E.Artacho, J.D.Gale, A.Garcia, J.Junquera,  
P.Ordejon, D.Sanchez-Portal and J.M.Soler.

The first versions of ggaxc and cellxc routines were written by 
C.Balbas, J.L.Martins, and J.M.Soler, 1996. Other parts of ggaxc
were originally written by M.V.Fernandez-Serra, J.Ferrer, 
V.M.Garcia-Suarez, and M.Machado (1998-2006).

siestaXC contains some code based on Numerical Recipes, The art of
Scientific Computing, W.H.Press, S.A.Teukolsky, W.T.Vetterlink, and
B.P.Flannery, Cambridge U.P. 1988 and 1992.

